snippet.title: Arcade Spirits: The New Challengers - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1484620/Arcade_Spirits_The_New_Challengers/

Arcade Spirits: The New Challengers is the follow-up to 2019's Arcade Spirits, a visual novel of love and pixels, in which you seek friendship and romance while working in an arcade. Now the tables are turned, as you seek friendship and romance while PLAYING in an arcade!

http://arcadespirits.com/newchallengers/

Follow PQube Games on social media!
Discord: https://discord.gg/pqubegames 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pqubegames/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PQubeGames 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/pqubegames/

#VisualNovel #genderneutral #Romance #friendship #ArcadeSpirits #arcade
